<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="vi">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>
        <%= title %> | Hệ thống Quản lý Đào tạo
    </title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Nunito:wght@300;400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root {
            --sidebar-width: 280px;
            --topbar-height: 70px;
            --primary-color: #4e73df;
            --primary-gradient: linear-gradient(to right, #1a237e, #283593);
            --secondary-color: #f8f9fc;
            --text-dark: #5a5c69;
            --card-shadow: 0 0.5rem 1rem rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
            --hover-transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Nunito', sans-serif;
            background-color: #f3f4f6;
            color: var(--text-dark);
        }

        .wrapper {
            display: flex;
            width: 100%;
            align-items: stretch;
        }

        .sidebar {
            min-width: var(--sidebar-width);
            max-width: var(--sidebar-width);
            background: var(--primary-gradient);
            color: #fff;
            transition: var(--hover-transition);
            height: 100vh;
            position: fixed;
            z-index: 100;
            box-shadow: 3px 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }

        .sidebar.collapsed {
            margin-left: calc(-1 * var(--sidebar-width));
        }

        .sidebar .sidebar-header {
            padding: 1.5rem 1rem;
            text-align: center;
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .sidebar .sidebar-header h3 {
            margin: 0;
            font-weight: 800;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        .sidebar ul.components {
            padding: 1rem 0;
            margin: 0;
        }

        .sidebar ul li {
            list-style: none;
            position: relative;
        }

        .sidebar ul li a {
            padding: 0.8rem 1.5rem;
            display: block;
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85);
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: var(--hover-transition);
            font-weight: 500;
            border-left: 3px solid transparent;
        }

        .sidebar ul li a:hover {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            color: #ffffff;
            border-left-color: #ffffff;
        }

        .sidebar ul li a i {
            margin-right: 10px;
            width: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
        }

        .sidebar ul li.active a {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.18);
            color: #ffffff;
            border-left-color: #ffffff;
        }

        .sidebar ul.collapse {
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            padding-left: 1rem;
        }

        .content {
            width: 100%;
            min-height: 100vh;
            transition: all 0.3s;
            margin-left: var(--sidebar-width);
        }

        .content.full-width {
            margin-left: 0;
        }

        .topbar {
            height: var(--topbar-height);
            background: #fff;
            box-shadow: 0 .15rem 1.75rem 0 rgba(58, 59, 69, .15);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 0 1rem;
            position: fixed;
            width: calc(100% - var(--sidebar-width));
            z-index: 99;
        }

        .topbar.full-width {
            width: 100%;
        }

        .topbar-nav {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            width: 100%;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .sidebar-toggle {
            background: none;
            border: none;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            color: var(--text-dark);
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        .user-info {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .user-info img {
            width: 40px;
            height: 40px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            margin-right: 10px;
        }

        .main-content {
            padding: calc(var(--topbar-height) + 1.5rem) 1.5rem 1.5rem 1.5rem;
        }

        .card {
            border: none;
            box-shadow: 0 0.5rem 1rem rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
            border-radius: 0.75rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
        }

        .card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 0.75rem 1.5rem rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12);
        }

        .card-header {
            background-color: #f8f9fc;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e3e6f0;
            padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            border-radius: 0.75rem 0.75rem 0 0 !important;
        }

        .card-header h5 {
            margin: 0;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #4e73df;
        }

        .table-responsive {
            overflow-x: auto;
        }

        .table {
            width: 100%;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            color: #212529;
            border-collapse: separate;
            border-spacing: 0 0.5rem;
        }

        .table th {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #5a5c69;
            background-color: #f8f9fc;
            border-top: none;
            padding: 1rem;
        }

        .table td {
            padding: 1rem;
            vertical-align: middle;
            border-top: none;
            background-color: white;
        }

        .action-buttons .btn {
            margin-right: 5px;
        }

        .btn-sm {
            padding: 0.4rem 0.8rem;
            font-size: 0.875rem;
            border-radius: 50px;
            transition: all 0.2s;
        }

        .btn-primary {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4e73df, #224abe);
            border: none;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(78, 115, 223, 0.2);
        }

        .btn-primary:hover {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #224abe, #1a3a8e);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 15px rgba(78, 115, 223, 0.3);
        }

        .btn-warning {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f6c23e, #dda20a);
            border: none;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(246, 194, 62, 0.2);
        }

        .btn-warning:hover {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #dda20a, #c69500);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 15px rgba(246, 194, 62, 0.3);
        }

        .btn-danger {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e74a3b, #c23321);
            border: none;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(231, 74, 59, 0.2);
        }

        .btn-danger:hover {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #c23321, #9d1f11);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 15px rgba(231, 74, 59, 0.3);
        }

        .filter-row {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .badge-dalen {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #28a745, #1f8836);
        }

        .badge-daky {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #17a2b8, #117a8b);
        }

        .badge-hoanthi {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #dc3545, #bd2130);
        }

        .modal-header {
            background: var(--primary-gradient);
            color: white;
        }

        .modal-content {
            border-radius: 0.75rem;
            border: none;
            box-shadow: 0 0.5rem 1rem rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
        }

        .footer {
            padding: 1.5rem;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: #858796;
            margin-top: 2rem;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="wrapper">
        <!-- Sidebar -->
        <nav id="sidebar" class="sidebar">
            <div class="sidebar-header">
                <h3>Quản lý Đào tạo</h3>
            </div>

            <ul class="components">
                <li>
                    <a href="/taikhoan/admin/dashboard"><i class="fas fa-tachometer-alt"></i> Bảng điều khiển</a>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <a href="#userSubmenu" data-bs-toggle="collapse" aria-expanded="false" class="dropdown-toggle">
                        <i class="fas fa-users"></i> Quản lý người dùng
                    </a>
                    <ul class="collapse list-unstyled" id="userSubmenu">
                        <li>
                            <a href="/taikhoan/admin/manage-admins"><i class="fas fa-user-shield"></i> Quản trị viên</a>
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <a href="/taikhoan/admin/manage-students"><i class="fas fa-user-graduate"></i> Sinh viên</a>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <a href="/taikhoan/admin/manage-news"><i class="fas fa-newspaper"></i> Quản lý tin tức</a>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <a href="#courseSubmenu" data-bs-toggle="collapse" aria-expanded="false" class="dropdown-toggle">
                        <i class="fas fa-book"></i> Quản lý học phần
                    </a>
                    <ul class="collapse list-unstyled" id="courseSubmenu">
                        <li>
                            <a href="/taikhoan/admin/manage-courses"><i class="fas fa-list"></i> Đăng ký học phần</a>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <a href="/taikhoan/admin/manage-grades"><i class="fas fa-clipboard-list"></i> Quản lý điểm</a>
                </li>
                <li class="active">
                    <a href="#scheduleSubmenu" data-bs-toggle="collapse" aria-expanded="true" class="dropdown-toggle">
                        <i class="fas fa-calendar-alt"></i> Lịch học - Lịch thi
                    </a>
                    <ul class="collapse show list-unstyled" id="scheduleSubmenu">
                        <li>
                            <a href="/taikhoan/admin/lichhoc"><i class="fas fa-calendar-day"></i> Lịch học</a>
                        </li>
                        <li class="active">
                            <a href="/taikhoan/admin/lichthi"><i class="fas fa-calendar-check"></i> Lịch thi</a>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <a href="/taikhoan/admin/taichinh"><i class="fas fa-money-bill-wave"></i> Quản lý tài chính</a>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <a href="/taikhoan/admin/settings"><i class="fas fa-cog"></i> Cài đặt hệ thống</a>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <a href="/taikhoan/dang-xuat"><i class="fas fa-sign-out-alt"></i> Đăng xuất</a>
                </li>
            </ul>
        </nav>

        <!-- Page Content -->
        <div id="content" class="content">
            <nav class="topbar">
                <div class="topbar-nav">
                    <button type="button" id="sidebarCollapse" class="sidebar-toggle">
                        <i class="fas fa-bars"></i>
                    </button>
                    <div class="user-info">
                        <img src="/images/default-avatar.png" alt="Admin Avatar">
                        <div>
                            <span>Xin chào, Admin</span>
                            <div class="small">
                                <%= user.email %>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </nav>

            <div class="main-content">
                <div class="container-fluid">
                    <h1 class="h3 mb-4 text-gray-800">Quản lý Lịch Thi</h1>

                    <% if (typeof error !=='undefined' && error) { %>
                        <div class="alert alert-danger alert-dismissible fade show">
                            <i class="fas fa-exclamation-circle me-2"></i>
                            <%= error %>
                                <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="alert"></button>
                        </div>
                        <% } %>

                            <% if (typeof success !=='undefined' && success) { %>
                                <div class="alert alert-success alert-dismissible fade show">
                                    <i class="fas fa-check-circle me-2"></i>
                                    <%= success %>
                                        <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="alert"></button>
                                </div>
                                <% } %>

                                    <!-- Add Exam Form Card -->
                                    <div class="card shadow mb-4">
                                        <div class="card-header">
                                            <h5 class="card-title mb-0">Thêm Lịch Thi Mới</h5>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="card-body">
                                            <form id="addExamForm" action="/taikhoan/admin/lichthi/them" method="POST"
                                                class="row g-3">
                                                <div class="col-md-4">
                                                    <label for="mahocphan" class="form-label">Học Phần</label>
                                                    <select class="form-select" id="mahocphan" name="mahocphan"
                                                        required>
                                                        <option value="">Chọn học phần</option>
                                                        <% if (courses && courses.length> 0) { %>
                                                            <% courses.forEach(course=> { %>
                                                                <option value="<%= course.mahocphan %>">
                                                                    <%= course.mahocphan %> - <%= course.tenhocphan %>
                                                                </option>
                                                                <% }); %>
                                                                    <% } %>
                                                    </select>
                                                </div>
                                                <div class="col-md-4">
                                                    <label for="namhoc" class="form-label">Năm Học</label>
                                                    <select class="form-select" id="namhoc" name="namhoc" required>
                                                        <option value="">Chọn năm học</option>
                                                        <% const currentYear=new Date().getFullYear(); for (let i=0; i <
                                                            5; i++) { const year=currentYear + i - 2; const
                                                            academicYear=`${year}-${year+1}`; %>
                                                            <option value="<%= academicYear %>" <%=i===2 ? 'selected'
                                                                : '' %>>
                                                                <%= academicYear %>
                                                            </option>
                                                            <% } %>
                                                    </select>
                                                </div>
                                                <div class="col-md-4">
                                                    <label for="kihoc" class="form-label">Kỳ Học</label>
                                                    <select class="form-select" id="kihoc" name="kihoc" required>
                                                        <option value="">Chọn kỳ học</option>
                                                        <option value="1">Học kỳ 1</option>
                                                        <option value="2">Học kỳ 2</option>
                                                        <option value="3">Học kỳ 3</option>
                                                    </select>
                                                </div>
                                                <div class="col-md-4">
                                                    <label for="thu" class="form-label">Thứ</label>
                                                    <select class="form-select" id="thu" name="thu" required>
                                                        <option value="">Chọn thứ</option>
                                                        <option value="Thứ 2">Thứ 2</option>
                                                        <option value="Thứ 3">Thứ 3</option>
                                                        <option value="Thứ 4">Thứ 4</option>
                                                        <option value="Thứ 5">Thứ 5</option>
                                                        <option value="Thứ 6">Thứ 6</option>
                                                        <option value="Thứ 7">Thứ 7</option>
                                                        <option value="Chủ Nhật">Chủ Nhật</option>
                                                    </select>
                                                </div>
                                                <div class="col-md-4">
                                                    <label for="thoigianthi" class="form-label">Thời Gian Thi</label>
                                                    <input type="datetime-local" class="form-control" id="thoigianthi"
                                                        name="thoigianthi" required>
                                                </div>
                                                <div class="col-md-4">
                                                    <label for="phongthi" class="form-label">Phòng Thi</label>
                                                    <input type="text" class="form-control" id="phongthi"
                                                        name="phongthi" placeholder="Nhập phòng thi" required>
                                                </div>
                                                <div class="col-md-4">
                                                    <label for="giangviencoithi" class="form-label">Giảng Viên Coi
                                                        Thi</label>
                                                    <input type="text" class="form-control" id="giangviencoithi"
                                                        name="giangviencoithi" placeholder="Nhập tên giảng viên coi thi"
                                                        required>
                                                </div>
                                                <div class="col-md-4">
                                                    <label for="hinhthuathi" class="form-label">Hình Thức Thi</label>
                                                    <select class="form-select" id="hinhthuathi" name="hinhthuathi"
                                                        required>
                                                        <option value="">Chọn hình thức thi</option>
                                                        <option value="Tự luận">Tự luận</option>
                                                        <option value="Trắc nghiệm">Trắc nghiệm</option>
                                                        <option value="Vấn đáp">Vấn đáp</option>
                                                        <option value="Thực hành">Thực hành</option>
                                                        <option value="Trực tuyến">Trực tuyến</option>
                                                    </select>
                                                </div>
                                                <div class="col-md-4">
                                                    <label for="trangthai" class="form-label">Trạng Thái</label>
                                                    <select class="form-select" id="trangthai" name="trangthai"
                                                        required>
                                                        <option value="đã lên lịch" selected>Đã lên lịch</option>
                                                        <option value="đã hoàn thành">Đã hoàn thành</option>
                                                        <option value="hoãn thi">Hoãn thi</option>
                                                    </select>
                                                </div>
                                                <div class="col-md-12">
                                                    <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary mt-3">Thêm Lịch
                                                        Thi</button>
                                                </div>
                                            </form>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>

                                    <!-- Exam List Card -->
                                    <div class="card shadow mb-4">
                                        <div class="card-header">
                                            <h5 class="card-title mb-0">Danh Sách Lịch Thi</h5>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="card-body">
                                            <% if (typeof tableExists==='undefined' || tableExists) { %>
                                                <div class="row filter-row">
                                                    <div class="col-md-3">
                                                        <input type="text" id="searchInput" class="form-control"
                                                            placeholder="Tìm kiếm...">
                                                    </div>
                                                    <div class="col-md-3">
                                                        <select id="courseFilter" class="form-select">
                                                            <option value="">Tất cả học phần</option>
                                                            <% if (courses && courses.length> 0) { %>
                                                                <% courses.forEach(course=> { %>
                                                                    <option value="<%= course.mahocphan %>">
                                                                        <%= course.mahocphan %> - <%= course.tenhocphan
                                                                                %>
                                                                    </option>
                                                                    <% }); %>
                                                                        <% } %>
                                                        </select>
                                                    </div>
                                                    <div class="col-md-2">
                                                        <input type="date" id="dateFilter" class="form-control"
                                                            placeholder="Ngày thi">
                                                    </div>
                                                    <div class="col-md-2">
                                                        <select id="roomFilter" class="form-select">
                                                            <option value="">Tất cả phòng thi</option>
                                                            <% if (rooms && rooms.length> 0) { %>
                                                                <% rooms.forEach(room=> { %>
                                                                    <option value="<%= room.phongthi %>">
                                                                        <%= room.phongthi %>
                                                                    </option>
                                                                    <% }); %>
                                                                        <% } %>
                                                        </select>
                                                    </div>
                                                    <div class="col-md-2">
                                                        <select id="statusFilter" class="form-select">
                                                            <option value="">Tất cả trạng thái</option>
                                                            <option value="đã lên lịch">Đã lên lịch</option>
                                                            <option value="đã hoàn thành">Đã hoàn thành</option>
                                                            <option value="hoãn thi">Hoãn thi</option>
                                                        </select>
                                                    </div>
                                                </div>

                                                <div class="table-responsive">
                                                    <table class="table table-bordered table-hover"
                                                        id="examSchedulesTable">
                                                        <thead class="table-light">
                                                            <tr>
                                                                <th>STT</th>
                                                                <th>Mã học phần</th>
                                                                <th>Tên học phần</th>
                                                                <th>Năm học</th>
                                                                <th>Kỳ học</th>
                                                                <th>Ngày thi</th>
                                                                <th>Giờ thi</th>
                                                                <th>Phòng thi</th>
                                                                <th>Giảng viên coi thi</th>
                                                                <th>Hình thức thi</th>
                                                                <th>Trạng thái</th>
                                                                <th>Thao tác</th>
                                                            </tr>
                                                        </thead>
                                                        <tbody>
                                                            <% if (examSchedules && examSchedules.length> 0) { %>
                                                                <% examSchedules.forEach((schedule, index)=> {
                                                                    const examDate = new Date(schedule.thoigianthi);
                                                                    const formattedDate =
                                                                    examDate.toLocaleDateString('vi-VN');
                                                                    const formattedTime =
                                                                    examDate.toLocaleTimeString('vi-VN', {
                                                                    hour: '2-digit', minute: '2-digit' });

                                                                    let statusClass = '';
                                                                    if (schedule.trangthai === 'đã lên lịch')
                                                                    statusClass =
                                                                    'bg-primary';
                                                                    else if (schedule.trangthai === 'đã hoàn thành')
                                                                    statusClass =
                                                                    'bg-success';
                                                                    else if (schedule.trangthai === 'hoãn thi')
                                                                    statusClass =
                                                                    'bg-danger';
                                                                    %>
                                                                    <tr>
                                                                        <td>
                                                                            <%= index + 1 %>
                                                                        </td>
                                                                        <td>
                                                                            <%= schedule.mahocphan %>
                                                                        </td>
                                                                        <td>
                                                                            <%= schedule.tenhocphan %>
                                                                        </td>
                                                                        <td>
                                                                            <%= schedule.namhoc %>
                                                                        </td>
                                                                        <td>
                                                                            <%= schedule.kihoc %>
                                                                        </td>
                                                                        <td>
                                                                            <%= formattedDate %>
                                                                        </td>
                                                                        <td>
                                                                            <%= formattedTime %>
                                                                        </td>
                                                                        <td>
                                                                            <%= schedule.phongthi %>
                                                                        </td>
                                                                        <td>
                                                                            <%= schedule.giangviencoithi %>
                                                                        </td>
                                                                        <td>
                                                                            <%= schedule.hinhthuathi %>
                                                                        </td>
                                                                        <td>
                                                                            <span class="badge <%= statusClass %>">
                                                                                <%= schedule.trangthai %>
                                                                            </span>
                                                                        </td>
                                                                        <td class="action-buttons">
                                                                            <button
                                                                                class="btn btn-sm btn-primary edit-exam"
                                                                                data-id="<%= schedule.id %>">Sửa</button>
                                                                            <button
                                                                                class="btn btn-sm btn-danger delete-exam"
                                                                                data-id="<%= schedule.id %>"
                                                                                data-course="<%= schedule.tenhocphan %>">Xóa</button>
                                                                        </td>
                                                                    </tr>
                                                                    <% }); %>
                                                                        <% } else { %>
                                                                            <tr>
                                                                                <td colspan="12" class="text-center">
                                                                                    Chưa có dữ liệu lịch thi</td>
                                                                            </tr>
                                                                            <% } %>
                                                        </tbody>
                                                    </table>
                                                </div>
                                                <% } else { %>
                                                    <div class="alert alert-warning">
                                                        <h4 class="alert-heading">Bảng dữ liệu lịch thi chưa được tạo!
                                                        </h4>
                                                        <p>Bảng dữ liệu "lichthi" chưa tồn tại trong cơ sở dữ liệu. Bạn
